    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-8075-b9d3-ef9abc6b7ea7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Online features a very high dropout rate and, for that reason, tools for proper recommendations and tutoring are welcomed. Authors explore how item-response theory can be integrated into a recommender. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-8075-b9d3-ef9abc6b7ea7",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
